Package CashItems

Class Item

java.lang.Object
CashItems.Item
public class Item extends Object
This class represents a TYPE of item, it is intended to be used as a programmatic type, much like pythonic tuples. As such it is an IMMUTABLE type, and cannot be changed after creation
